== Battle Commands ==

=== Move ===

* Robots move on grid
* Speed determines distance
* Position affects targeting

=== Attack ===

* Basic physical strike
* Uses equipped weapon
* Range varies by weapon type

=== Run ===

* Flee the battle
* Success varies by speed

=== Program ===

* Use programmed abilities
* Consumes energy
* Various effects

